---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About FlowOP | Your Silent Partner in Performance"
  description="20+ years in planning, supply chain, logistics, and operational finance helping growing teams align systems with execution."
  pathname="/about"
  bodyClass="about-page"
>
  <main>
    <section class="about-hero" aria-labelledby="about-hero-heading">
      <div class="about-hero-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="container about-hero-inner">
        <span class="hero-eyebrow about-hero-eyebrow reveal">About <span class="brand-mark">FlowOP</span></span>
        <h1 id="about-hero-heading" class="about-hero-title reveal">
          Built for teams growing into more complexity than their <em class="about-title-accent">systems can handle.</em>
        </h1>
        <p class="about-hero-lead reveal">
          After 20+ years across planning, supply chain, logistics, and operational finance, I’ve seen how quickly
          strong teams lose confidence when reporting, planning, and delivery stop moving together.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-why" aria-labelledby="about-why-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-why-grid">
          <div class="about-why-copy">
            <p class="about-why-kicker reveal">— Why <span class="brand-mark">FlowOP</span> exists</p>
            <h2 id="about-why-heading" class="about-why-title reveal">
              Practical systems support before you need a full <em class="about-title-accent">ops department.</em>
            </h2>
            <p class="about-why-intro reveal">
              Growing businesses need operational clarity before they’re ready for a full-time hire. That’s the gap I fill: fractional, focused, and built to hand over cleanly.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="about-why-quotes">
            <div class="about-quote reveal">
              <p>
                I help teams reconnect how decisions are made, how plans are set, and how work is executed.
                <strong>Start with one focused sprint, then build only what the business truly needs next.</strong>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-bring" aria-labelledby="about-bring-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <header class="about-bring-header reveal">
          <p class="about-bring-kicker">What I bring</p>
          <h2 id="about-bring-heading" class="about-bring-title">
            Deep experience in the failure points that hurt growth first.
          </h2>
          <p class="about-bring-lead">
            Twenty years across the functions where operational complexity tends to compound fastest.
          </p>
        </header>
        <div class="about-bring-frame reveal">
          <div class="about-bring-grid">
            <article class="about-bring-card">
              <span class="about-bring-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="7.25" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"></circle>
                  <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"></circle>
                  <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="0.9" fill="currentColor"></circle>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <h3>Planning</h3>
              <p>Capacity, demand, inventory, and scheduling work that supports better day-to-day decisions.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="about-bring-card">
              <span class="about-bring-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path
                    d="M4 10A6 6 0 0 1 14.5 6"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.6"
                    stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                  <path
                    d="M16 10A6 6 0 0 1 5.5 14"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.6"
                    stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                  <path
                    d="M14.5 6V3.5M14.5 6H12"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.6"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                  <path
                    d="M5.5 14V16.5M5.5 14H8"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.6"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <h3>Supply Chain</h3>
              <p>Operational structure that helps supply, inventory, and execution stay aligned as the business grows.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="about-bring-card">
              <span class="about-bring-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path
                    d="M3.5 10H16"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.6"
                    stroke-linecap="round"></path>
                  <path
                    d="M11.5 5.5L16 10L11.5 14.5"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.6"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <h3>Logistics &amp; Workflows</h3>
              <p>Process redesign that removes friction, clarifies handoffs, and makes work easier to run under pressure.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="about-bring-card">
              <span class="about-bring-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <rect x="3.25" y="3.25" width="13.5" height="13.5" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"></rect>
                  <path d="M3.5 8.25H16.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"></path>
                  <path d="M8.25 8.25V16.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.6"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <h3>Reporting &amp; Analytics</h3>
              <p>Decision-ready reporting, dashboards, and operating visibility that leaders can trust.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="about-bring-card">
              <span class="about-bring-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path
                    d="M3 7.5C5 5.5 6.5 5.5 8.5 7.5C10.5 9.5 12 9.5 14 7.5"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.6"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                  <path
                    d="M3 12.5C5 10.5 6.5 10.5 8.5 12.5C10.5 14.5 12 14.5 14 12.5"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.6"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <h3>Operational Finance</h3>
              <p>Better structure around the numbers that shape planning, priorities, and execution tradeoffs.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="about-bring-card">
              <span class="about-bring-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path
                    d="M11 2.5L4.5 11.5H9.5L8.5 17.5L15.5 8.5H10.5L11 2.5Z"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-width="1.6"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    fill="none"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              <h3>Automation &amp; Systems</h3>
              <p>Less manual handling, fewer fragile workarounds, and systems designed to scale with the business.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="about-work" aria-labelledby="about-work-heading">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="about-work-grid">
          <div class="about-work-copy">
            <p class="about-work-kicker reveal">How I work</p>
            <h2 id="about-work-heading" class="about-work-title reveal">
              Understand quickly. Align clearly. <em class="about-title-accent">Leave teams with ownership.</em>
            </h2>
            <p class="about-work-intro reveal">
              I run FlowOP on a fractional model — one dedicated day per week, with sprint-time support where the
              business case is clear.
            </p>
          </div>
          <ol class="about-work-steps reveal">
            <li class="about-work-step">
              <span class="about-work-num" aria-hidden="true">1</span>
              <div class="about-work-step-body">
                <h3>Practical First</h3>
                <p>The work has to be usable in the real business, not just sound good in theory.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="about-work-step">
              <span class="about-work-num" aria-hidden="true">2</span>
              <div class="about-work-step-body">
                <h3>Scoped Clearly</h3>
                <p>Engagements start with clear priorities, defined outcomes, and realistic timelines agreed upfront.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="about-work-step">
              <span class="about-work-num" aria-hidden="true">3</span>
              <div class="about-work-step-body">
                <h3>Built to Scale</h3>
                <p>Start with an alignment sprint, then expand support only where it adds clear operational value.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="about-work-step">
              <span class="about-work-num" aria-hidden="true">4</span>
              <div class="about-work-step-body">
                <h3>Remote by Default</h3>
                <p>Most delivery is remote. Client or on-site visits are planned in advance around key milestones.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-banner" aria-labelledby="about-cta-heading">
      <div class="container cta-banner-inner">
        <h2 id="about-cta-heading" class="cta-banner-title reveal">
          If your team needs systems that match <em class="cta-banner-accent">the pace of growth.</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="cta-banner-lead reveal">
          Start with a discovery call. We’ll scope the right first sprint together — no obligation, just clarity.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-banner-actions reveal">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://calendly.com/flowopsolutions-calendar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Book Discovery Call</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/services">View Services</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
